FROM (

    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Content], [p].[DateCreated], [p].[DateModified], [p].[Description], [p].[HomeFlag], [p].[HotFlag], [p].[Image], [p].[Name], [p].[OriginalPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[PromotionPrice], [p].[SeoAlias], [p].[SeoDescription], [p].[SeoKeywords], [p].[SeoPageTitle], [p].[Status], [p].[Tags], [p].[Unit], [p].[ViewCount]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE CAST(1 AS bit) = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p0] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p1] ON [p0].[Id] = [p1].[CategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
